{"tid":2142067,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"被國安法通輯 陳家駒：不會放棄爭取香港獨立","createTime":"2020-08-06T06:59:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-06T11:58:31.000Z","uid":70063,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"cc4ab79b561341c949b7a7752277e141d7dd257e","tid":2142067,"uid":70063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T06:59:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=188992726151460&amp;id=100706081646792\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D188992726151460%26id%3D100706081646792&d=il%2BrReVPph3FBkDtfLAFOkWuH9aop70KQP2vpO%2BUA2I%3D&h=5379a7b6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=188992726151460&amp;id=100706081646792</a><br />\n<br />\n我不會因離開改變我的政治主張，尤其是在香港的人，之後未必能隨心所欲表達所思所想。<br />\n<br />\n緊隨過去一年的政治動盪，陳預測可能會有另一波移民潮，將代表他倡導工作的關鍵時機，因為獨立將發展為海外香港人最終目標：&ldquo;作為流亡者，我對返回香港的信念十分堅定。 散居海外的社區最終會代表港人，繼續進行國際遊說。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n被問及他何時認為可以安全返回香港時，他說：&ldquo;十年之內，我相信我會回到香港。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hongkongfp.com/2020/08/03/exclusive-wanted-by-beijing-activist-in-exile-wayne-chan-says-he-wont-stop-fighting-for-hong-kong-independence/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhongkongfp.com%2F2020%2F08%2F03%2Fexclusive-wanted-by-beijing-activist-in-exile-wayne-chan-says-he-wont-stop-fighting-for-hong-kong-independence%2F&d=il%2BrReVPph3FBkDtfLAFOkWuH9aop70KQP2vpO%2BUA2I%3D&h=1dcfcaaf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hongkongfp.com/2020/08/03/exclusive-wanted-by-beijing-activist-in-exile-wayne-chan-says-he-wont-stop-fighting-for-hong-kong-independence/</a>"},{"pid":"1b45e4f8517e5f70b49e1430f09a0892b6403cbe","tid":2142067,"uid":53036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T06:59:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fro